snippet.title: Child Of Ault - Early Access Trailer [VR, HTC Vive]
snippet.description:
Early Access trailer for Child Of Ault, a virtual reality tower defense game. Developed by Hangzhou NezhaGames, available for HTC Vive. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/child-of-ault
